      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ILLBERIDINGSHOTGUN (3) is a two-year-old colt by Bettors Wish on debut for Chantal Turpin. Looked above average in winning his latest trial at this circuit and distance and a nice draw on the front line should ensure a cosy run so he could kick off with a win. SWEET TIMES (6) drew on the back row and was outclassed in a Breeders Classic final last start but did well to place in his heat prior. He will enjoy a class drop. STUNNING STRANGER NZ (5) was beaten only 3.5m at his most recent appearance at Redcliffe and came from a similar barrier to this when he missed by a nose here prior. Contender. SWEET CHARMER (2) draws well and must be included after he raced parked but fought well to go under by a head last start",
